Package com.google.appinventor.components.runtime.collect

Utilities providing static methods used by component code for working with collections.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Lists
    Provides static methods for creating List instances easily, and other utility methods for working with lists.
    Maps
    Provides static methods for creating mutable Maps instances easily.
    Sets
    Provides static methods for creating mutable Set instances easily and other static methods for working with Sets.
